subtitle: David do you think anything in the Bible
can be taken literally any of the
stories but when you look at it ancient
peoples thought differently than we do
we are very left brain in our current
society and so we take everything

then we look at it as it's written and
it becomes very literal for us but in
the ancient mind they did not think like
